name: Diamond - Spider
description:
Karakurt Spider- 1 of 10 art from the "Diamond Animals" collection. Karakurt is a species of black widow spider. The ancient Indian tradition calls the creator of all things Brahma - a spider that weaves the world from a web-matter. This diamond karakurt can create the most incredible worlds.
